                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>San Francisco</placeName>\n                <date>Sep 5, 1855</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">During my<lb/> absence from here <persName>Dr. Eckman</persName>\n                paid<lb/> me for the Occident; please acknow-<lb/>-ledge the same. Your Books\n                shipped<lb/> pr. ship “Snap Dragon” have not arrived yet. If they were<lb/> here\n                now, I could readily dispose of<lb/> them, being near our Holidays.<lb/> My\n                principal object to write you with<lb/> this mail is to inform you of an\n                organization<lb/> of a charitable society that is in the act of<lb/> being formed by\n                our Jewish Ladies in this<lb/> city. A Number of Ladies <del>assembled</del><lb/>\n                met for the first time at <persName>Mr. Jacob<lb/> Rich's</persName> House &amp;\n                organized the society,<lb/> of which <persName>Mrs. Abm. Tandler</persName> acted\n                the<lb/> President &amp; <persName>Mrs. Rich</persName> secretary. A<lb/> subsequent\n                meeting was then called in<lb/> the synagogue of the Congregation of Emanu-<lb/>-El\n                on <date><sic>sunday</sic> the 5<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> of <sic>aug.</sic></date>\n                when a<lb/> large numer of Ladies were present. The object<lb/> &amp; importance of\n                the Benefit</p>\n            <div>\n                <p>\n                    <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_13_9.pdf\">The above text refers to Occident\n                        Volume 13 No. 9 page 419. Click here to view.</ref>\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3cj8858c/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
